viewdefs.ExchangeIn:
<viewdef type="form" name="ExchangeIn" class="edu.ku.brc.specify.datamodel.ExchangeIn" gettable="edu.ku.brc.af.ui.forms.DataGetterForObj" settable="edu.ku.brc.af.ui.forms.DataSetterForObj">
            <desc>ExchangeIn viewing form.</desc>

            <columnDef>105px,2px,170px,5px,125px,2px,150px,5px,96px,2px,170px,0px,15px,p,p:g</columnDef>
            <columnDef os="lnx">115px,2px,185px,5px,150px,2px,165px,5px,101px,2px,185px,0px,15px,p,p:g</columnDef>
            <columnDef os="mac">130px,2px,204px,5px,170px,2px,183px,5px,126px,2px,203px,0px,15px,p,p:g</columnDef>
            <columnDef os="exp">p,2px,p:g(2),5px:g,p,2px,p:g(2),5px,p:g,2px,p:g(2),0px,p,p:g</columnDef>
            <rowDef auto="true" cell="p" sep="1dlu" />

            <rows>
                <row>
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="1" />
                    <cell type="field" id="1" name="exchangeInNumber" uitype="formattedtext" />
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="7" />
                    <cell type="field" id="7" name="quantityExchanged" uitype="text" />
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="9" />
                    <cell type="field" id="9" name="exchangeDate" uitype="formattedtext" uifieldformatter="Date" default="Today" />
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="2" />
                    <cell type="field" id="2" name="agentCatalogedBy" uitype="querycbx" initialize="name=Agent" colspan="3" />
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="3" />
                    <cell type="field" id="3" name="agentReceivedFrom" uitype="querycbx" initialize="name=Agent" colspan="3" />
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="4" />
                    <cell type="field" id="4" name="descriptionOfMaterial" uitype="text" colspan="9" />
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="5" />
                    <cell type="field" id="5" name="remarks" uitype="textareabrief" rows="2" colspan="10" />
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell type="subview" id="6" name="addressOfRecord" viewname="AddressOfRecord" colspan="13" />
                </row>
                
            </rows>
        </viewdef>
